{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2021-02-06-what-happend-when-a-pod-is-created.markdown/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<!-- vim-markdown-toc Redcarpet -->\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">前言</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B\">过程</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93\">小结</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!-- vim-markdown-toc -->\n<h1>前言</h1>\n<p>当 k8s 创建一个 pod 时，发生了什么？</p>\n<h1>过程</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>kubectl apply -f nginx.yaml</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">apiVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> apps/v1 <span class=\"token comment\"># for versions before 1.9.0 use apps/v1beta2</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">kind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Deployment\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">metadata</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nginx<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>deployment\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">spec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">selector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">matchLabels</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">app</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nginx\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">replicas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># tells deployment to run 2 pods matching the template</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">metadata</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">labels</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">app</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nginx\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">spec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">containers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nginx\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nginx<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>1.14.2\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">ports</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">containerPort</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">80</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">---</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">apiVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> v1\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">kind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Service\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">metadata</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nginx\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">labels</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nginx\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">spec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">ports</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">port</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">80</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">protocol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> TCP\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">selector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nginx</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>APIServer 收到消息，把 Pod 信息存到 ETCD</p>\n<p>2.1 身份验证(authentication)</p>\n<p>2.2 授权验证(RBAC)是否有 create、delete、list 等权限</p>\n<p>2.3 进入到 Mutation Admission Controller，修改 yaml</p>\n<p>2.4 Schema validaion 检验上一步修改后的 yaml 时候正确</p>\n<p>2.5 Validation Admission Controller 检验资源用量等</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>调度器指定 Node,修改 Pod 信息将 node 信息绑定,并更新到 ETCD 里</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>kubelet 创建 Pod</p>\n<p>4.1 CRI 创建 contaier</p>\n<p>4.2 CNI 创建 container 网络并指定 IP</p>\n<p>4.3 CSI 创建存储、挂载文件</p>\n<p>4.4 检查 livenessProbe 和 readinessProbe</p>\n<p>4.5 上报 pod 信息，到 ETCD</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>如果 pod 属于 Service，接下来会创建 endpoint，通过组合 IP:PORT 暴露服务</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Endpoints 被用于</p>\n<p>6.1 kube-proxy 设置 iptables 规则</p>\n<p>6.2 CornDNS 更新 DNS 条目</p>\n<p>6.3 Ingress controllers 设置 downstreams</p>\n<p>6.4 Service meshes(Istio)</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>小结</h1>\n<p>本篇简单介绍一下 pod 创建的流程，后续会再写文章对一些步骤进行解析。如自定义 Mutation Admission 和 Validation Admission、CNI、CSI、CRI 等。</p>\n<h1>Reference</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/danielepolencic/status/1291371746801545219?s=21\">https://twitter.com/danielepolencic/status/1291371746801545219?s=21</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://draveness.me/kubernetes-pod/\">https://draveness.me/kubernetes-pod/</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">前言</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B\">过程</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93\">小结</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"当 k8s 创建一个 pod 时，发生了什么？","date":"2021-02-06"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2021-02-06-what-happend-when-a-pod-is-created.markdown"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"],"slicesMap":{}}